LUCKY pupils from Cleeves Primary School, in Barrhead were on a tasty assignment. Tasty world of Primary 6 LUCKY pupils from Cleeves Primary School, in Barrhead were on a tasty assignment.The P6 youngsters learned how to prepare the world on a plate at Cook &amp; Indi's World Buffet in Darnley.Amongst the dishes the pupils prepared were pizza, curry and special fried rice. 